From dfd93588aba874ad92af38d9d31fbe54bc7ded13 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Max Bachmann <oss@maxbachmann.de>
Date: Sun, 18 Jan 2026 19:04:14 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 11/36] Add Ubuntu {18.04,20.04,22.04,24.04} configs on x86_64

Versions for libc and the kernel headers were verified with the following methods:

libc: podman run --rm ubuntu:20.04 ldd --version
kernel: podman run --rm ubuntu:20.04 /bin/bash -c "apt update -qq && apt install -y -qq linux-libc-dev > /dev/null && dpkg -l linux-libc-dev"

Signed-off-by: Max Bachmann <oss@maxbachmann.de>
